Rabawa manyan fayiloli / fayiloli - wadannan su ne manyan fayiloli / files cewa ba su bukatar mai amfani da Tantance kalmar sirri *, wanda ke nufin cewa su suna samuwa ga dukan baƙi * (idan suna da link). Duk da haka, shared manyan fayiloli iya samun iyaka izini: Don loda, downloading, files / manyan fayiloli list. Below ne mai tebur na links to shared manyan fayiloli / files halitta by users. Don aiki jama'a links ƙunshi daidai tabbata cewa handlers \ Anonymousdownload.ashx damar m damar yin amfani da IIS. Za ka iya duba wannan a kan kanikancin page. Tabbatar cewa m user account sanya handlers \ Anonymousdownload.ashx yana NTFS reading / rubuce-rubuce izini saboda shared manyan fayiloli / files.
*   &mdash.   idan ba ka saka masu amfani, ga abin da kawai aka yarda access.

Localization.AdminUpdateMainInfo: Wannan irin da haɓaka da aka partially sarrafa kansa. Za ka iya ƙirƙira da sauke madadin fayil da aikace-aikace saitunan sanyi da kuma mayar da shi bayan da haɓaka. Ka bi wadannan short matakai: ƙirƙirar madadin fayil, yi da manual da haɓaka, mayar da saituna daga madadin fayil. Wannan hanya kuma za a iya amfani da su madadin / mayar da saituna ba tare da haɓaka. Kawai tsallake da haɓaka mataki don maido da saituna daga madadin fayil.
Localization.AdminUpdateAutoInfo: Wannan irin da haɓaka kusan ya cika sarrafa kansa. Yana kunshi 2 matakai: madadin na yanzu saituna (ya kamata ka saukewa da ajiyewa a fayil madadin), shigarwa na wani sabon version da maido da saituna daga madadin fayil. HTTP Kwamandan iya ta atomatik download da latest version kuma shigar da shi ko za ka iya saka da hanya zuwa zip archive da sabon version a kan uwar garke. All saituna ta atomatik mayar daga baya halitta madadin fayil.
